      "page_number": 1,
      "raw_text": "Judge KEENAN, yesterday granted\npermission to Nettie j. Bolbow,\nwidow of one Of the Great North\nern wreck victims at Camden, to\nsettle for $4,000.\n\n\nKEN Kobubow, japanese stu\ndent, has been placed on the wait\ning list for employment by the\nGreat Northern as engineer and\ncraftsman.\n\n\nAdjustment will be made in a\nfew days of the claims of the es-\ntates Of I. M. Cornthwait and w.\nF. Townsend, killed in the recent\nwreck of the S. F. & N. at Waneta,\nb. G."
    }
